Class AppEngineCredentialStore

Beta
Thread-safe Google App Engine implementation of a credential store that directly uses the App Engine Data Store API. @since 1.7 @author Yaniv InbarInbar @deprecated (scheduled to be removed in 1.17) Use AppEngineDataStoreFactory with StoredCredential instead, optionally using .migrateTo(AppEngineDataStoreFactory) or .migrateTo(DataStore) to migrating an existing AppEngineCredentialStore.
